#. Tag: title
#: resizehowto.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "How-To: Resizing a Partition"
msgstr "Navodila: Spreminjanje velikosti particije"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This how-to explains the resizing of a <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-"
"partition\">partition</glossterm> that is becoming too full. See the "
"following screenshot for the initial situation before resizing:"
msgstr ""
"Ta navodila pojasnjujejo spreminjanje velikosti <glossterm linkend="
"\"glossary-partition\">particije</glossterm>, ki postaja prepolna. Oglejte "
"si naslednji posnetek zaslona za začetno situacijo pred spreminjanjem "
"velikosti:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window before resizing partitions"
msgstr "Glavno okno pred spreminjanjem velikosti particij"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-device\">device</glossterm> <quote>/dev/"
"sdb</quote>, partition <quote>sdb2</quote> has only little free space left "
"while the other partition, <quote>sdb1</quote>, is far from being full. For "
"that reason it seems advisable to make the first partition a little smaller "
"and grow <quote>sdb2</quote> so it has more free space available."
msgstr ""
"Na <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-device\">napravi</glossterm> <quote>/dev/"
"sdb</quote> ima particija <quote>sdb2</quote> le malo prostega prostora, "
"druga particija, <quote >sdb1</quote>, še zdaleč ni polns. Zaradi tega se "
"zdi priporočljivo narediti prvo particijo nekoliko manjšo in povečati "
"<quote>sdb2</quote>, da bo imela na voljo več prostega prostora."

#. Tag: title
#: resizehowto.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note: You cannot modify mounted partitions."
msgstr "Opomba: ne morete spreminjati priklopljenih particij."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the screenshot above both partitions are not currently mounted. If one or "
"both of them were mounted you would have to unmount them first using <xref "
"linkend=\"menu-partition-mount\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Na zgornjem posnetku zaslona obe particiji trenutno nista priklopljeni. Če "
"bi bili priklopljeni ena ali obe, bi ju morali najprej odklopiti z <xref "
"linkend=\"menu-partition-mount\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step is to make more room for the partition to grow, so start by "
"shrinking <quote>sdb1</quote>. Click on the partition and choose <xref "
"linkend=\"menu-partition-resize\"/>. The following dialog comes up:"
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak je narediti več prostora za rast particije, zato začnite s "
"krčenjem <quote>sdb1</quote>. Kliknite na particijo in izberite <xref "
"linkend=\"menu-partition-resize\"/>. Prikaže se naslednje pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize dialog before resizing /dev/sdb1"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno pred spreminjanjem velikosti /dev/sdb1"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dialog allows you to resize the partition in multiple ways. You can "
"either drag the right handle to the left until the partition has the desired "
"size or simply enter the size in the <guilabel>Size</guilabel> text field. "
"Another possibility would be to adjust the size by clicking on the little "
"arrows next to the text field, but that is a little tedious for larger "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno vam omogoča spreminjanje velikosti particije na več načinov. "
"Desni ročaj lahko povlečete v levo, dokler particija ne doseže želene "
"velikosti, ali preprosto vnesete velikost v besedilno polje "
"<guilabel>Velikost</guilabel>. Druga možnost bi bila prilagoditev velikosti "
"s klikom na majhne puščice poleg besedilnega polja, vendar je to za večje "
"spremembe nekoliko dolgotrajno."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whichever way you prefer for setting the new size, the dialog should now "
"look like this:"
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na način, na katerega želite nastaviti novo velikost, bi moralo "
"biti pogovorno okno zdaj videti takole:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize dialog after resizing /dev/sdb1"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno po spremembi velikosti /dev/sdb1"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you click on <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, a new operation is added to "
"the pending operations list and the graphical view and tree view of the "
"device are updated to reflect the new situation:"
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, se na seznam čakajočih operacij "
"doda nova operacija, grafični in drevesni pogled naprave pa se posodobita, "
"da odražata novo situacijo:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window after resizing /dev/sdb1"
msgstr "Glavno okno po spremembi velikosti /dev/sdb1"

#. Tag: title
#: resizehowto.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note: Operations are previewed first before applying them."
msgstr ""
"Opomba: Operacije si najprej ogledate v predogledu, preden jih uveljavite."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although the main window reflects the device's state how it will be after "
"applying the new operation, the operation has in fact not been applied yet: "
"While operations are pending you can still undo them (one by one using <xref "
"linkend=\"menu-edit-undo\"/> or <xref linkend=\"menu-edit-clear\"/> to undo "
"all of them) or quit &partman;, and nothing will have been modified at all."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav glavno okno odraža stanje naprave, kakšno bo po uporabi nove "
"operacije, operacija dejansko še ni bila uveljavljena: medtem ko so "
"operacije v teku, jih lahko še vedno razveljavite (eno za drugo z <xref "
"linkend=\"menu-edit-undo\"/> ali <xref linkend=\"menu-edit-clear\"/> za "
"razveljavitev vseh) ali zapustite &partman; in nič ne bo spremenjeno."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that there is some free space between the two partitions you can move "
"and grow partition <quote>sdb2</quote>. First, click on <quote>sdb2</quote> "
"and choose <xref linkend=\"menu-partition-resize\"/> again. The resize "
"dialog comes up once more, this time for the second partition. Drag its left "
"handle to the leftmost end so that the dialog looks like this:"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko je med dvema particijama nekaj prostega prostora, lahko premaknete "
"in povečate particijo <quote>sdb2</quote>. Najprej kliknite <quote>sdb2</"
"quote> in znova izberite <xref linkend=\"menu-partition-resize\"/>. Ponovno "
"se prikaže pogovorno okno za spreminjanje velikosti, tokrat za drugo "
"particijo. Povlecite njen levi ročaj na skrajni levi konec, tako da bo "
"pogovorno okno videti takole:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize dialog after resizing /dev/sdb2"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno po spremembi velikosti /dev/sdb2"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful to make sure that the <guilabel>Free space before</guilabel> text "
"field really does show <quote>0 MiB</quote> because otherwise there will be "
"a little free space left between the partitions that will then be wasted."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da besedilno polje <guilabel>Prosti prostor pred</guilabel> "
"res prikazuje <quote>0 MiB</quote>, ker bo drugače med particijami ostalo "
"malo prostega prostora, ki bo nato izgubljen."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> again. In the main window things now "
"look like this:"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj znova kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>. V glavnem oknu so stvari "
"zdaj videti takole:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window after resizing /dev/sdb2"
msgstr "Glavno okno po spremembi velikosti /dev/sdb2"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This already looks like what you wanted, so choose <xref linkend=\"menu-edit-"
"apply\"/>. A dialog box will come up and ask you if you are sure to apply "
"the pending operations. Confirm this dialog box and &partman; will begin "
"executing operations:"
msgstr ""
"To je že videti tako, kot ste želeli, zato izberite <xref linkend=\"menu-"
"edit-apply\"/>. Pojavi se pogovorno okno in vas vpraša, ali ste prepričani, "
"da boste uporabili čakajoče operacije. Potrdite to pogovorno okno in "
"&partman; bo začel izvajati operacije:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "&partman; is applying operations"
msgstr "&partman; uveljavlja operacije"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While operations are being executed you can click on the plus-sign next to "
"each operation in the list to find out the jobs it is made up of and see "
"which job is currently being run."
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko se operacije izvajajo, lahko kliknete znak plus poleg vsake "
"operacije na seznamu, da ugotovite, iz katerih opravil je sestavljena, in "
"vidite, katero opravilo se trenutno izvaja."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resizing a partition in the way you resized <quote>/dev/sdb2</quote> above "
"always means it has to be moved to the left first before it can be grown "
"because partitions can never be grown to the left directly. Unfortunately, "
"moving such a large partition will take quite some time. It is not unusual "
"for an operation like this to take several minutes or even more."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje velikosti particije na način, kot ste spremenili velikost "
"<quote>/dev/sdb2</quote> zgoraj, vedno pomeni, da jo je treba najprej "
"premakniti v levo, preden jo lahko povečate, ker particije nikoli ni mogoče "
"povečati neposredno v levo. Na žalost bo premikanje tako velike particije "
"trajalo kar nekaj časa. Ni nenavadno, da takšen poseg traja nekaj minut ali "
"celo več."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finally, all operations will have been successfully completed:"
msgstr "Končno bodo vse operacije uspešno zaključene:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Progress dialog after successfully applying operations"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno napredka po uspešni uporabi operacij"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking on <guibutton>OK</guibutton> you can now close the progress "
"dialog and return to the main window. &partman; will rescan your devices at "
"this point so that might take a few seconds."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> lahko zdaj zaprete pogovorno okno "
"napredka in se vrnete v glavno okno. &partman; bo na tej točki znova "
"pregledal vaše naprave, kar lahko traja nekaj sekund."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are interested in some more details about the operations that were "
"just run click on <guibutton>Details</guibutton>. You will see the detailed "
"report that is always generated (and updated on the fly) while &partman; "
"executes operations:"
msgstr ""
"Če vas zanima več podrobnosti o pravkar zagnanih operacijah, kliknite "
"<guibutton>Podrobnosti</guibutton>. Videli boste podrobno poročilo, ki se "
"vedno ustvari (in sproti posodablja), medtem ko &partman; izvaja operacije:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: resizehowto.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Progress dialog details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti pogovornega okna napredka"

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This report is particularly of interest if an error occurs while executing "
"operations. A report shows each operation, each job and each external "
"command that is being run and is thus very helpful when trying to track down "
"problems."
msgstr ""
"To poročilo je še posebej zanimivo, če pride do napake med izvajanjem "
"operacij. Poročilo prikazuje vsako operacijo, vsako opravilo in vsak zunanji "
"ukaz, ki se izvaja, in je zato zelo koristno pri odkrivanju težav."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can save the report as <acronym>HTML</acronym> or view it in an external "
"web browser."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo lahko shranite kot <acronym>HTML</acronym> ali si ga ogledate v "
"zunanjem spletnem brskalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Always save the detailed report as <acronym>HTML</acronym> when executing "
"the operations fails with errors or warnings for later reference. You might "
"also want to include it in a bug report you submit to the &kde; bug tracking "
"system at <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org\">bugs.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Vedno shranite podrobno poročilo kot <acronym>HTML</acronym>, ko izvajanje "
"operacij ne uspe z napakami ali opozorili za kasnejšo uporabo. Morda ga "
"boste želeli vključiti tudi v poročilo o napakah, ki ga oddate v &kde; "
"sistem za sledenje hroščem na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org\">bugs.kde."
"org</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: resizehowto.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To hide the details again click on <guibutton>Details</guibutton> and to "
"finally close the progress dialog click on <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite znova skriti podrobnosti, kliknite <guibutton>Podrobnosti</"
"guibutton> in za končno zapiranje pogovornega okna napredka kliknite "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."
